This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to extract relational facts from text. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses pre-trained language models and fine-tuning techniques, which are common in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with classification and prediction tasks, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
